# AI Clause Risk Analyzer (Upload-ready GitHub Project)

This project extracts clauses/paragraphs from a PDF contract/RFP and classifies risk levels (Low/Medium/High) with risk type + mitigation suggestions.

Works out of the box (rule-based baseline)  
Optional OpenAI support for richer explanations (set OPENAI_API_KEY)

---

## Features
- PDF upload
- Text extraction (PyPDF)
- Clause/paragraph splitting
- Risk classification (baseline rules)
- Optional LLM-enhanced reasoning/explanations
- FastAPI endpoint + Swagger UI

